PC0

interface eth0
 ip address 192.168.1.31
 subnet mask 255.255.255.0
 default gateway 192.168.1.1
----------------------------------------
PC1

interface eth0
 ip address 192.168.1.32
 subnet mask 255.255.255.0
 default gateway 192.168.1.1


Additional Notes:
+DNS lookup is disabled on all routers and switches using no ip domain-lookup.
+The passwords for console and VTY lines are set to "cisco" as per the requirements.
+The configurations for RIP routing protocol are included to enable routing between the networks.
+EtherChannel is set up on the switches to bundle GigabitEthernet0/3 and GigabitEthernet0/4 interfaces into Port-channel1.
+HSRP configuration is not included because it was not specified in the provided instructions.
